com.tgerm.tolerado.axis14.core.sobject
Class ToleradoSobject

java.lang.Object
  com.tgerm.tolerado.axis14.core.sobject.ToleradoSobject

public class ToleradoSobject
extends java.lang.Object

An intelligent wrapper over SObject that makes easy to perform create and updates. It also boosts performance by caching the MessageElement instances intelligently, so fetching values is faster.

Author:
abhinav

getUpdatedSObject

public com.sforce.soap.partner.sobject.SObject getUpdatedSObject()

getNestedSObject
